OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fsome sunny spells at first but
OL,7,Fgenerally turning cloudier through the
OL,8,Fevening. Remaining largely dry and
OL,9,Fcloudy overnight with just a few brief
OL,10,Fclearer intervals.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA dry and cloudy start, then
OL,13,Fcloud gradually breaking up through
OL,14,Fthe day to give some long sunny spells
OL,15,Fin the afternoon.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,18,Flargely dry and settled few days with
OL,19,Fthe odd spot of rain possible at
OL,20,Ftimes. Cloudy at times but still
OL,21,Fplenty of bright or sunny spells.
